---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Systems Integration | Jay Software - Connect & Automate Your Business"
  description="Stop wasting 20+ hours/week on manual data entry. Connect disconnected systems, automate workflows, save 15-25 hours weekly, and increase accuracy by 95%. ROI in 3-6 months."
  keywords="systems integration, business automation, workflow automation, data integration, API integration, CRM integration, ERP integration, legacy system modernization"
  canonicalUrl="https://jay-software.com/services/systems-integration"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-900/20 to-orange-900/20 border-b border-slate-700">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-600/20 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            🔗 Systems Integration
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Stop Wasting <span class="text-red-400">20+ Hours/Week</span> on
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              Manual Data Entry
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Connect your disconnected systems, eliminate manual work, and automate workflows. Save 15-25 hours/week and increase accuracy by 95%.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/#strategic-consultation" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 hover:from-amber-700 hover:to-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Get Systems Analysis
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problems Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Are Disconnected Systems <span class="text-red-400">Killing</span> Your Productivity?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            Most businesses waste 20+ hours weekly on manual data entry, duplicate work, and system switching...
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">⌚</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Time Wasted on Manual Work</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Employees spend hours copying data between systems instead of focusing on revenue-generating activities.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">❌</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Human Errors Everywhere</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Manual data entry leads to costly mistakes, customer issues, and compliance problems.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🏝️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Data Silos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Critical business information trapped in separate systems, preventing informed decisions.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">📊</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">No Real-Time Visibility</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Outdated reports and delayed insights causing missed opportunities and poor decisions.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🔄</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Duplicate Workflows</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Same work being done multiple times across different systems and departments.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">💸</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Hidden Operational Costs</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Inefficiencies adding up to thousands in lost productivity and missed revenue monthly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
              Seamless System Integration That <span class="text-amber-400">Actually Works</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Connect all your business systems into one unified, automated workflow that saves time and eliminates errors.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-amber-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Save 15-25 Hours/Week</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Eliminate manual data entry and redundant workflows through smart automation.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">95% Error Reduction</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Automated data sync prevents human errors and ensures data consistency.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Real-Time Insights</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Unified dashboards with live data from all systems for better decision-making.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-purple-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">ROI in 3-6 Months</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Integration pays for itself quickly through time savings and improved efficiency.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Systems We Connect:</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">CRM systems (Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">ERP systems (SAP, NetSuite, QuickBooks)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">E-commerce platforms (Shopify, WooCommerce)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Marketing tools (Mailchimp, Klaviyo, Google Ads)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Legacy systems & custom databases</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Cloud services (AWS, Azure, Google Cloud)</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Integration Types -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            <span class="text-orange-400">Complete Integration Solutions</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            From simple API connections to complex enterprise integrations
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-amber-400 text-3xl mb-4">🔌</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">API Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Connect modern systems through REST APIs, webhooks, and real-time data sync.</p>
            <div class="text-green-400 font-semibold">2-4 weeks</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-blue-400 text-3xl mb-4">🗄️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Database Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Sync data between multiple databases, data warehouses, and legacy systems.</p>
            <div class="text-green-400 font-semibold">3-6 weeks</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-green-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-green-400 text-3xl mb-4">🔄</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Workflow Automation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Automate business processes across multiple systems and departments.</p>
            <div class="text-green-400 font-semibold">4-8 weeks</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-purple-400 text-3xl mb-4">☁️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Cloud Migration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Move legacy systems to cloud and integrate with modern platforms.</p>
            <div class="text-green-400 font-semibold">6-12 weeks</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-3xl mb-4">📊</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Data Analytics Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Connect all data sources to business intelligence and reporting tools.</p>
            <div class="text-green-400 font-semibold">3-6 weeks</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-indigo-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-indigo-400 text-3xl mb-4">🏢</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">Enterprise Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Complex multi-system integrations for large organizations.</p>
            <div class="text-green-400 font-semibold">8-16 weeks</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Studies -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Integration Success Stories
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            How businesses saved thousands of hours with smart integrations
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Distribution Company</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Integrated ERP, CRM, and inventory management systems</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center mb-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-400">30hrs</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Weekly Time Savings</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">95%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Error Reduction</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">$180K</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Annual Savings</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic">
              "The integration eliminated 90% of our manual data entry and gave us real-time visibility across all operations."
            </blockquote>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Marketing Agency</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Connected client reporting tools with campaign management systems</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center mb-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">25hrs</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Weekly Time Savings</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">80%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Faster Reporting</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">350%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">ROI Increase</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic">
              "Automated reporting freed up our team to focus on strategy instead of spreadsheets. Client satisfaction increased 40%."
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-900/20 to-orange-900/20 border-t border-slate-700">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Ready to <span class="text-amber-400">Eliminate Manual Work</span> Forever?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Stop wasting time on data entry. Get seamless system integration that automates your workflows.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/#strategic-consultation" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 hover:from-amber-700 hover:to-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Get Systems Analysis
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
              </svg>
              Back to Home
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout> 